    <section class="about-me-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>About Me</h2>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <img src="img/about-me.jpg" alt="About Me" class="img-fluid">
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-8">
                    <p>Welcome to Bima Creations, where gaming meets creativity. I’m Nathan Machoka, the founder and editor of this gaming website. With a passion for gaming, a love of ancient civilizations, and a desire to explore my creative potential, I started Bima Creations to share my love for games and provide an update about the first game I've ever created.</p>
                    <p>Currently, I’m immersed in the development of my first gaming project, "The Maze." While it's still a work in progress with some features yet to be perfected, it’s been an exciting journey into the roots of 3D game design. I chose to build "The Maze" using SDL2 and raycasting technology to honor the classic era of gaming, reminiscent of titles like Wolfenstein and the original DOOM. This foundational experience is helping me lay the groundwork before I dive into more modern technologies such as OpenGL and Unity.</p>
		    <p>At Bima Creations, I’m dedicated to creating a space where gamers can explore the latest trends, dive into detailed reviews, and connect with a community of enthusiasts. Join me as I continue to develop "The Maze," learn, and share my progress. Thank you for being part of this exciting adventure!</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
